OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FHousehold water bills in England and
OL,7,FWales will increase by an average of
OL,8,F#31 a year over the next five years,
OL,9,Fregulator Ofwat has announced.
OL,11,FThe proposed bill rise is
OL,12,Fsignificantly higher than the expected
OL,13,Faverage increase of around #20 a year
OL,14,Fper household, outlined in the
OL,15,Fregulator's draft proposals in July.
