OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FMost providers also have other schemes
OL,7,Fin place to support people who are
OL,8,Fstruggling to afford their water bills.
OL,10,FFor example, Thames Water can provide
OL,11,Fa 50% discount on water bills if your
OL,12,Fannual household income is less than
OL,13,F#21,740, or place an annual cap on
OL,14,Fcosts, while Severn Trent can offer up
OL,15,Fto 70% off water bills if you earn
OL,16,Fless than #20,048 a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
