OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FAll homes built since 1990 should have
OL,7,Fa water meter, and if not you can get
OL,8,Fone installed for free.
OL,10,FThe CCW has an online tool you can use
OL,11,Fto calculate whether you would benefit
OL,12,Ffrom having a water meter installed,
OL,13,Fand your water company should also be
OL,14,Fable to let you know whether it is
OL,15,Fworth getting a meter.
OL,17,FIn Scotland water bills are based on
OL,18,Fcouncil tax bands, while there are no
OL,19,Fdomestic charges for water in Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
