OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FWhat if you stop paying?
OL,8,FIt is always best to speak to your
OL,9,Fprovider if you are having trouble
OL,10,Fpaying your bills to negotiate an
OL,11,Falternative payment plan than
OL,12,Fknowingly not paying for your water.
OL,14,FIf you do leave a water bill unpaid,
OL,15,Fyour provider will send one or more
OL,16,Freminder notices, with a final notice
OL,17,Fgiving you seven days to pay.
OL,19,FThe company may phone you to ask for
OL,20,Fpayment, or they could pass your debt
OL,21,Fonto a debt recovery agent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
