OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FAs a last resort a company may take
OL,7,Fyou to court to recover the money
OL,8,Fowed. This could then lead to bailiff
OL,9,Faction in the most extreme cases.
OL,11,FCan your water be cut off?
OL,13,FCompanies cannot legally disconnect or
OL,14,Frestrict the water supply to your
OL,15,Fhome, even if you owe them money.
OL,17,FThe rules can vary for business water
OL,18,Fsupplies.
